# Some transitive dependencies pulled in by @privy-io/react-auth v3
# (e.g. @wallet-standard/app -> node >=22, graphql-ws -> node >=20) declare
# stricter Node engine ranges than our build environment (Node 20). These are
# declaration-only constraints — the packages run correctly on Node 20 — so we
# skip yarn's engine check to keep CI and Vercel installs from failing.
ignore-engines true
